quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,"Observe strictly the prayers, and the middle prayer, and stand up full of devotion towards God"
  2,239,"And if you have any alarm, then pray on foot or riding: but when you are safe, then remember God, how he hath made you to know what ye knew not"
  2,240,"And such of you as shall die and leave wives, shall bequeath their wives a year's maintenance without causing them to quit their homes; but if they quit them of their own accord, then no blame shall attach to you for any disposition they may make of themselves in a fair way. And God is Mighty, Wise"
  2,241,And for the divorced let there be a fair provision. This is a duty in those who fear God
  2,242,Thus God maketh his signs clear to you that ye may understand
  2,243,"Hast thou not thought on those who quitted their dwellings - and they were thousands - for fear of death? God said to them, \"Die:\" then He restored them to life, for full of bounty towards man is God. But most men give not thanks"
  2,244,"Fight for the cause of God; and know that God is He who Heareth, Knoweth"
  2,245,"Who is he that will lend to God a goodly loan? He will double it to him again and again: God is close, but open handed also: and to Him shall ye return"